{
  "texts": [
    "The experimental data is then provided, followed by additional analysis.",
    "Deepfake DatasetFaceForensics (FF + +) [59], DeepFakeTIMIT [60], DeepFakes Detection Challenge Preview (DFDCpre) [61], and CelebDF [62] were the datasets used in the research.",
    "FaceForensics + + is a big dataset for face modification detection that is utilized in deepfake detection.",
    "Also, FaceSwap, DeepFakes, Face2Face, and NeuralTextures are deepfake techniques for constructing artificial faces.",
    "There are more than 1000 deepfake videos in each category."
  ]
